  "doc_id": "prion_0782",
  "text": "The case reported here is that of a 50-year-old man from Saltillo, Coahuila, Mexico, who during the previous 15 months developed a demential syndrome and myoclonia.\nThe brain biopsy led to establish a diagnosis of spongiform encephalopathy.\nThe EEG showed periodic sharp wave complexes over the right hemisphere.\nA review on about prion diseases is included.",
